Package org.tedros.fx.animation

Class ElasticInterpolator

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.animation.Interpolator
      • org.tedros.fx.animation.EasingInterpolator
        • org.tedros.fx.animation.ElasticInterpolator
  • public class ElasticInterpolator
extends EasingInterpolator
    This interpolator simulates an elastic behavior.

    The following curve illustrates the interpolation.

    The math in this class is taken from http://www.robertpenner.com/easing/.

    Author:
    Christian Schudt
